00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.000
And these were the same qualities

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.000
that I looked for in my own husband,

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:37.000
Barack Obama.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:41.000
